      "HSC is a civil engineering company that does infrastructure for the nation. We provide services to lay various types of utilities like gas, water, district cooling, power cables and telecom. Our staff actually face a large variety of problems on a day-to-day basis. Of course, we have the option of uh asking the more senior project managers or the project managers on what is the resolutions to such issue. But due to clashing schedules, this often can take up to 3 days to resolve even a minor issue. So when issues start to snowball, this have larger implications to the project. Complaints from the public will actually damage HSC's reputation as a reliable civil engineering company. If the field tasks are not completed, they will snowballs into delay and causing the project timeline to sleep.",
